            "contentType": "interactive",
            "images": [],
            "interactiveContent": "<!DOCTYPE html ><html><body><p>Esta lista contém filmes como <code>\"Vertigo\"</code> e datas de lançamento como <code>1958</code>, mas não está claro qual data pertence a qual filme.</p><code version=\"2\" codelang=\"python\" name=\"script.py\" visible-if=\"always\"><content><text value=\"movies = [\" /><text value=\"&quot;Vertigo&quot;\" class=\"string\" /><text value=\", \" /><text value=\"&quot;Parasite&quot;\" class=\"string\" /><text value=\", \" /><text value=\"1958\" class=\"number\" /><text value=\", \" /><text value=\"2019\" class=\"number\" /><text value=\"]\" /></content><interactions><interaction type=\"fillTheGap\" isDefault=\"true\"><options><option startIndex=\"10\" endIndex=\"19\" /><option startIndex=\"37\" endIndex=\"38\" /></options></interaction></interactions></code><p visible-if=\"wrong\">Certifique-se de escolher <code>\"Vertigo\"</code> seguido de <code>,</code>.</p></body></html>"
          },
          {
            "title": "Intro 2",
            "id": 88424,
            "contentType": "interactive",
            "images": [],
            "interactiveContent": "<!DOCTYPE html ><html><body><p>Podemos agrupar pedaços relacionados de dados com uma <strong>tupla</strong>, como em <code>movie_tuples</code> aqui, que agrupa nomes de filmes e datas de lançamento juntos.</p><code version=\"2\" codelang=\"python\" name=\"script.py\" visible-if=\"always\"><content><text value=\"movies = [\" /><text value=\"&quot;Vertigo&quot;\" class=\"string\" /><text value=\", \" /><text value=\"&quot;Parasite&quot;\" class=\"string\" /><text value=\", \" /><text value=\"1958\" class=\"number\" /><text value=\", \" /><text value=\"2019\" class=\"number\" /><text value=\"]\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"movie_tuples = [(\" /><text value=\"&quot;Vertigo&quot;\" class=\"string\" /><text value=\", \" /><text value=\"1958\" class=\"number\" /><text value=\"), (\" /><text value=\"&quot;Parasite&quot;\" class=\"string\" /><text value=\", \" /><text value=\"2019\" class=\"number\" /><text value=\")]\" /></content><interactions><interaction type=\"fillTheGap\" isDefault=\"true\"><options><option startIndex=\"62\" endIndex=\"79\" /><option startIndex=\"79\" endIndex=\"80\" /></options></interaction></interactions></code><p visible-if=\"wrong\">Certifique-se de escolher <code>(\"Vertigo\", 1958)</code> seguido de <code>,</code>.</p></body></html>"
          },
          {
            "title": "Tuples",
            "id": 88353,
            "contentType": "interactive",
            "images": [],
            "interactiveContent": "<!DOCTYPE html ><html><body><p><strong>Tuplas</strong> nos ajudam a agrupar diferentes pedaços de dados que pertencem juntos, como na tupla <code>vertigo_data</code> aqui.</p><code version=\"2\" codelang=\"python\" name=\"script.py\" visible-if=\"always\"><content><text value=\"vertigo_data = (\" /><text value=\"&quot;Vertigo&quot;\" class=\"string\" /><text value=\", \" /><text value=\"1958\" class=\"number\" /><text value=\")\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"print(vertigo_data)\" /><text type=\"break\" /></content><interactions><interaction type=\"fillTheGap\" isDefault=\"true\"><options><option startIndex=\"0\" endIndex=\"12\" /><option correct=\"false\"><content><text value=\"print\" /></content></option></options></interaction></interactions><output><content><text value=\"('Vertigo', 1958)\" /></content></output></code><p visible-if=\"wrong\">Certifique-se de escolher <code>vertigo_data</code>.</p></body></html>"
          },
          {
            "title": "Parentheses",
            "id": 88354,
            "contentType": "interactive",
            "images": [],
            "interactiveContent": "<!DOCTYPE html ><html><body><p>Criamos tuplas de forma semelhante às listas, mas usamos parênteses <code>()</code> em vez de colchetes ao redor dos valores.</p><code version=\"2\" codelang=\"python\" name=\"script.py\" visible-if=\"always\"><content><text value=\"vertigo_data = (\" /><text value=\"&quot;Vertigo&quot;\" class=\"string\" /><text value=\", \" /><text value=\"1958\" class=\"number\" /><text value=\")\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"print(vertigo_data)\" /></content><interactions><interaction type=\"fillTheGap\" isDefault=\"true\"><options><option startIndex=\"15\" endIndex=\"16\" /><option startIndex=\"31\" endIndex=\"32\" /><option correct=\"false\"><content><text value=\",\" /></content></option></options></interaction></interactions><output><content><text value=\"('Vertigo', 1958)\" /></content></output></code><p visible-if=\"wrong\">Certifique-se de escolher <code>(</code> seguido de <code>)</code>.</p></body></html>"
